
ðŸ“¦ Button Types:---
| Button Type            | Description              | Example                   |
| ---------------------- | ------------------------ | ------------------------- |
| `Button`               | Default material button  | `Button {}`               |
| `OutlinedButton`       | Has an outlined border   | `OutlinedButton {}`       |
| `TextButton`           | No background or border  | `TextButton {}`           |
| `IconButton`           | Contains only an icon    | `IconButton {}`           |
| `FloatingActionButton` | Used for primary actions | `FloatingActionButton {}` |


ðŸ§  Key Button Properties Covered:--
| Property                                                             | Purpose                                  |
| -------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| `onClick`                                                            | Handles click action                     |
| `enabled`                                                            | Enables or disables the button           |
| `colors`                                                             | Customizes background and content colors |
| `elevation`                                                          | Provides shadow based on state           |
| `shape`                                                              | Rounded, circle, etc.                    |
| `modifier`                                                           | Adjusts size, padding, border, etc.      |
| `interactionSource`                                                  | Tracks interaction events                |
| `contentPadding`                                                     | Internal padding for content             |
| `Icon`, `Text`                                                       | Button content                           |
| `OutlinedButton`, `TextButton`, `IconButton`, `FloatingActionButton` | Specialized button types                 |

